  <brief_title>Characterization of Sweat Gland Function in Patients With Recessively Inherited Hypohidrotic Ectodermal Dysplasia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Validation of Non-invasive Technologies for the Characterization of Sweat Gland Function in Patients With Recessively Inherited Hypohidrotic Ectodermal Dysplasia, Their Heterozygous Family Members and Healthy Controls</official_title>
